javadoc: VersionedDBListener provides listeners the ability to be notified when changes occur to a versioned database.

methods.name: versionsChanged
methods.comment:
Available database versions have been modified.
 This method is not invoked when a new version is created.

methods.name: versionCreated
methods.comment: A new database version has been created.

return.comment:
true if version is allowed, if false is returned 
 the version will be removed.

 checkoutId is not valid.

Terminate the specified checkout.
